creator: Thrift+
descriptionHtml:
The new app to shop and donate the very best second-hand fashion.

With the Thrift+ App, you are able to:

SHOP:

- Shop the best brands. We hand pick the best donated fashion that is constantly updated on our app with 100s of items.

- Shop with confidence.
All items have been quality and authenticity checked, and come with our 30 day returns policy.

- Quickly find items you love.
Filter by category, style, size, condition and more.

- Stay updated. Receive notifications for weekly drops, special announcements and exclusive promotions.

**For app users only!*

*DONATE:

- Order a ThriftBag to donate your best second-hand clothes to raise funds for your favourite charity.

- Earn Thrift+ credits to spend online or exchange for a voucher with your favourite retailer.

- Manage your account and keep track of your donations.

- Get updates on your ThriftBag and live notifications as your items sell.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: Welcome to the new Thrift+ App!

title: Thrift+

creator: Thrift+
descriptionHtml:
Thrift+ is the pre-loved fashion marketplace. We want to end fashion waste. By making secondhand seamless.

Shop over 400,000 clothes from top high street and designer brands. All quality checked by us. All packaged and shipped by us. Moneyback guarantees and 30 day returns? Another plus.

Recirculate your pre-owned clothes and earn Thrift+ Points. We take care of the listing, packing and shipping.

We’re Thrift+. We love pre-loved.
